<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Crimble.com</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .features {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .feature-item {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to Crimble.com!</h1>
    <p>Your AI-Powered Job Platform</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello {{firstName}},</h2>
      
      <p>Welcome to Crimble.com! We're excited to have you join our platform as a {{role}}. With Crimble.com, you'll have access to powerful AI-driven tools that will help you streamline your job search or hiring process.</p>

      <div class="features">
        <h3>What you can do with Crimble.com:</h3>
        
        {{#if (eq role "employer")}}
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>AI-Powered Job Posting:</strong> Create compelling job descriptions with our AI assistant
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Smart Candidate Matching:</strong> Find the best candidates using our AI matching algorithm
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Interview Scheduling:</strong> Streamline your interview process with integrated scheduling
          </div>
        {{else if (eq role "jobseeker")}}
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>AI Job Matching:</strong> Get personalized job recommendations based on your profile
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Resume Optimization:</strong> Enhance your resume with AI-powered suggestions
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Interview Preparation:</strong> Practice with our AI interview coach
          </div>
        {{else}}
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Platform Management:</strong> Access powerful tools to manage the platform
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>Analytics Dashboard:</strong> Monitor platform performance and user engagement
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <strong>User Management:</strong> Manage users and their permissions
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>

      <p>To get started, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">Verify Email</a>
      </div>

      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our AI chatbot is available 24/7 to help you.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The Crimble.com Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© 2024 Crimble.com. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This email was sent to {{email}}. If you did not create an account with Crimble.com, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 